Shadow Ninja Knight : Fighting
Privacy Policy
At
Shadow Ninja Knight: Fighting
, we prioritize your privacy and the protection of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and the steps we take to ensure your data remains secure.
1. No Login Required
We do not require users to create an account or log in to play
Shadow Ninja Knight: Fighting
. As a result, we do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII), such as your name, email, or phone number.
2. No Ads
Our game is entirely ad-free, which means we do not use any third-party ad networks that may collect data for targeted advertising.
3. Data Collection and Usage
While no PII is collected,
Shadow Ninja Knight: Fighting
may collect non-personal data to improve the gameâ€™s performance, user experience, and for analytics purposes. The data we collect includes:
Gameplay Statistics:
Information about in-game progress, achievements, and player behavior to optimize the gaming experience.
Device Information:
Technical data such as your device type, operating system, and game version may be collected to troubleshoot bugs and enhance performance.
Crash Reports:
We may collect information when the game crashes, including device and game details, to help us fix issues.
4. In-Game Purchases
The game does not currently offer any in-game purchases. However, if in-game purchases are introduced in the future, this policy will be updated accordingly to explain how payment data is processed through third-party platforms (such as app stores), which we do not directly handle or store.
5. Data Sharing
We do not share your data with third-party companies, except when required by law or if we partner with analytics providers to improve game performance. These partners are subject to strict confidentiality agreements and may not use your data for any purposes other than those outlined in this Privacy Policy.
6. Data Retention
We retain gameplay data for as long as it is necessary to support the game and provide a seamless user experience. Non-personal data may be stored in anonymized formats for analytics purposes.
7. Security
We take reasonable steps to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, please note that no method of data transmission or storage is 100% secure.
8. Age Restrictions
Shadow Ninja Knight: Fighting
is designed for players aged 16 and above. We do not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 16.
9. Changes to This Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We encourage players to review this page periodically for any updates.
10. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
premiumqualityapps.com@gmail.com
.
